unt":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":297,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1484817306000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"林于丰","submitUpdateTime":"2017-01-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icvAJKfaPXrYVpc64VKYR3pcRQ6uiaXVZvPBEGwfTnp5t7b8qOZNmuJthzjTr4flT8pzXUuBEiaYgUg/0","content":"1、该参议员观点是站不住脚的，犯了滑坡谬误，将“可能发生的”转化为“必然发生的”。\n2、反驳理由：在自己的房间发生双方同意的同性性行为的人，不一定会重婚，多婚，乱伦，通奸和为所欲为，两者并没有必然发生的逻辑关系。\n3、反问：那你的意思是不是说如果国家剥夺了一个人在自己的房间里发生双方同意的同性性行为，那么重婚，多婚，乱伦，通奸的事情就会因此减少？请问你能保证吗？","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":174,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1484636844000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"pandada","submitUpdateTime":"2017-01-16","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ZoOhibBS4Niccib6WhTVxUibj7531TWPD55ic52pdc7uWQELib3ENKJaFv2Pic4NiaNaiaUZG1biafkOeCCYWkZJmNbcibhXH/0","content":"\n我认为他的言论站不住脚。这属于滑坡谬误。就算最高法院将同性性行为合法化，也没有证据证明重婚、通奸、乱伦等行为也将被合法化。这些行为之间没有必然的联系。\n\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":67,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1484558539000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":true},"code":200}
